\begin_layout Standard
Two points relevant for the computation:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
C_{\alpha}^{\left(2\right)}\left(t\right)\equiv\left\langle \sum_{\vec{x}}{\rm Tr}\left[S_{c}\left(x,0\right)\gamma_{\alpha}S_{q}\left(0,x\right)\gamma_{\alpha}\right]\right\rangle ,\quad\alpha\in\left\{ 1,\,2,\,3,\,5\right\} \,.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We define the spatial vector average:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\tilde{C}_{k}^{\left(2\right)}\left(t\right)=\frac{1}{3}\sum_{i=1}^{3}C_{i}^{\left(2\right)}\left(t\right)\,.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

